{"tid":639344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【水貨圍城】民建聯斥示威者是「香港之恥」","createTime":"2018-04-23T11:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T06:36:27.000Z","uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7daf5ead5ed4c86069499de2369f1e051e90975d","tid":639344,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"【水貨圍城】民建聯斥示威者是「香港之恥」<br />\n有內地人被示威者包圍指罵。<br />\n<br />\n本港多處昨日再有反水貨客示威，民建聯發聲明強烈譴責示威玷污香港，形容是香港之恥，又批評示威者是暴徒，以反水貨客為名在上水、屯門及尖沙咀聚眾生事，辱罵附近的居民及旅客。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯的聲明指，這批暴徒沿途叫囂，騷擾港人開設的店舖，令商戶無法營業，又毀壞市民手持的物品，有小孩更受驚哭泣，更推倒部分市民，擾亂香港秩序，破壞法治。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯促請警方果斷執法，嚴肅懲處所有參與暴行人士，包括在前線衝擊及幕後動員號召的人，又呼籲全港市民共同嚴斥暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20150309/53513595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150309%2F53513595&d=VtW5Q6rJdxxYGDK5MzSi3J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4e6056be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150309%2F53513595&h=72466eb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20150309/53513595</a>"},{"pid":"43cb06ddb874d688eee8a88a73801fa13554463e","tid":639344,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a38f2414e99f62a8f1d7ea6b47552484370e033","tid":639344,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63da771d9ec5a6842192e3b9e1556bb0d96964b7","tid":639344,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7801db9